<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tā shì jī dū 迦南642</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tā shì yé sū jī dū, tā shì fù huó de zhǔ. tā shì róng yào de zhǔ. tā shì dà néng de zhǔ.
 wǒ men dé yǐ áng shǒu, gāo guò sì miàn de chóu dí. yīn tā yǐ jīng fù huó, shèng guò hēi àn de quán shì.
 hā lì lù yà hā lì lù yà, hā lì lù yà hā lì lù yà,
 yīn tā yǐ jīng fù huó, shèng guò hēi àn de quán shì.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>642</hymn_number>
</song>